commit.message:
Add additional variants to linktype for the rel attribute

Implements the missing variants from the spec:
https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/links.html#linkTypes

Additionally, includes Me and Prerender variants, which are not listed in the
standard but listed in the MDN as important keywords:
https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Attributes/rel
